MIP
multum in parvo
"much in little"

plugin wrappers, abstractions, simplifications, helpers, ..

v0.0.0
in progress, prototype, proof of concept, pre-, ..

# os

- linux
- (windows)

# plugin

- exe
- clap
- vst2
- vst3
- (lv2)

# host

- clap
- (vst2)
- (vst3)

# gui

- xcb
- cairo
- (ctx)
- (gdi)

# other

- header-only
- low level, un-modern c++
- no weird/ugly build system
- few/no external dependencies
- 'fat' plugins (multiple plugin formats in one .so)
- sub-plugins
- etc, etc..

# plans, roadmap

- make it work
- make it right
- make it fast, small, stable, bugfree, pretty, etc..

